         <div xml:id="alalal-e94291"><!-- l3d26dt1 -->
            <head xml:id="alalal-e94291-Hd1e99">Divisio Textus</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e94291-d1e101">
               <cb ed="#Bd" n="b"/>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="10"/>DIVISIO TEXTUS.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e94291-d1e108">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="11"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-e94291-Qd1e112"> Est autem spes virtus qua spiritualia
<lb ed="Bd" n="12"/>et wterna bona speraniur, etc. </quote>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="13"/>Habito tractatu de fide, tangit hic in
<lb ed="Bd" n="14"/>una distinctione de spe, de qua 
determi<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="15"/>nat dupliciter, scilicet in se, et ex parte
<lb ed="Bd" n="16"/>sperantis, ibi, C, <quote xml:id="alalal-e94291-Qd1e126"> Post hoc superest 
in<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="17"/>vesiig are, etc, </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e94291-d1e132">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="18"/>In se autem tangit tria de spe, primo,
<lb ed="Bd" n="19"/>scilicet quid sit ? Et secundo, in quo 
con<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="20"/>venit cum fide, ibi, B, <quote xml:id="alalal-e94291-Qd1e140"> Et sicut fides,
<lb ed="Bd" n="21"/>tta et spes, etc.</quote> Tertio, in quo differt a
<lb ed="Bd" n="22"/>lide, ibi, B, ยง2: <quote xml:id="alalal-e94291-Qd1e148"> Distinguitur tamen
<lb ed="Bd" n="23"/>fides a spe, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-e94291-d1e154">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="24"/>Et ex hoc patet divisio. Sententia plana
<lb ed="Bd" n="25"/>est in Littera.
</p>
         </div>
